Package me.Abhigya.core.util.packet

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PacketListener
    Simple interface called when receiving or sending packets.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PacketAdapter
    Convenience implementation of PacketListener.
    PacketChannelHandler
    Simple player's channels handler, for handling the receiving-sending packets.
    PacketChannelHandler.PlayerChannelHandler
    The duplex channel handler for handling the packets when receiving or sending.
    PacketChannelHandler.PlayerInjector
    Listener that injects any player that joins the server.
    PacketChannelHandler.PlayerInjectorReflection
    Reflection class used by the PacketChannelHandler.PlayerInjector for getting the channel of a Player.
    PacketChannelHandler.RegisteredPacketListener
    Class representing the registered version of a PacketListener.
    PacketEvent
    Simple event called whenever a packet will be sent-received.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PacketListener.Priority
    Enumeration for Packet Event priority.
